## Final Capstone: The TaskFlow Codebase

Congratulations — you have reached the final exercise of the entire React Literacy course.

Here is the scenario: you have just joined a team that is building **TaskFlow**, a project management app. A developer hands you the codebase and says, "We have some bugs, some new features to plan, and some AI-generated code that needs review. Can you help?"

Below is the project. Take your time reading through it. This capstone tests everything you have learned across all eight levels.

